  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd 43 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc2\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Freedom Party and Champika's 43rd Brigade resolve to come together to prepare strategy for all-party government - Dayasiri",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "People who cannot participate in today's protest against the government in Colombo should participate in protests from their own places.",
        "Sri Lanka Freedom Party Secretary General Dayasiri Jayasekara said that the Freedom Party and the 43rd Brigade have decided to come together to prepare the strategy of the all-party government.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a press conference held at the office of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party.",
        "The government led by President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has no recognition among the people.",
        "The people's struggle against the government and the basic problems faced by the people are intensifying day by day and not diminishing. Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe mentions about the crises but does not get any solution to the problems.",
        "Those who cannot participate in today's protest against the government in Colombo should participate in protests from their own places. The democratic struggle will surely win.",
        "He said the 43rd Brigade of Member of Parliament Batali Sambika and the Independence Party are determined to prepare the framework for a one-fifth all-party government."
      ],
